<li>Fisher Stanley (Sir), <i>The Statute Laws of Cyprus: 1878 - 1923</i>, vol. I, London, 1923. </li>
<li>Howard Curtois John, Gerahty Cyril Charles., <i>The Statute Laws of Cyprus: 1878 - 1923</i>, vol. II, London, 1923. </li>
